\begin_layout Standard
\noindent
\align left
'
\begin_inset Formula $\implies$
\end_inset

' Supongamos que 
\begin_inset Formula $H\trianglelefteq G$
\end_inset

, sean 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in H/N,\ y\in G/N$
